  "prompt": "Where is good apartment near Deloitte Chicago?",
  "response": "Finding a good apartment near Deloitte in Chicago, which is located in the Willis Tower, will depend on your preferences, budget, and lifestyle. Here are some neighborhoods you might consider:\n\n1. **The Loop**: This is the central business district and offers a variety of upscale apartments and amenities. It's very convenient for commuting to Deloitte.\n\n2. **River North**: Known for its vibrant nightlife, art galleries, and restaurants, River North has many modern apartment options and is only a short walk from the Loop.\n\n3. **West Loop**: This trendy neighborhood has a mix of residential and commercial spaces, with plenty of dining options and a lively atmosphere. It's slightly further but still easily accessible.\n\n4. **South Loop**: This area offers more affordable options compared to the Loop and River North while maintaining proximity to downtown. The area is also home to parks and recreational spaces.\n\n5. **Streeterville**: Located just east of the Loop, Streeterville features luxury apartments and is close to Lake Michigan, offering beautiful views and parks.\n\nWhen searching for an apartment, consider factors such as commute times, public transportation access, amenities, and local services. Websites like Zillow, Apartments.com, and Trulia can be useful for browsing listings and comparing options. Additionally, working with a local real estate agent can provide valuable insights into the market.",
